8. Advantages

* Simple and easy to use
* Helps in financial awareness
* Efficient data storage using structures
* Quick analysis of expenses

---

9. Limitations

* Limited to 100 expenses
* No file storage (data lost after program ends)
* No graphical interface

---

10. Future Enhancements

